---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import site from '../site.config.json';
---
<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy -- Cloud Printing Australia" description="Privacy policy for cloudprinting.au. How we handle your personal information.">
  <section class="section-pad">
    <div class="container" style="max-width:760px">
      <h1 style="font-size:clamp(28px,4vw,40px);font-weight:800;margin-bottom:32px">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <div class="prose">
        <p><strong>Last updated:</strong> March 2026</p>
        <p>Cloud Printing Australia is operated by Voice Recognition Australia ABN [ABN]. This privacy policy explains how we collect, use, and protect personal information in accordance with the Australian Privacy Act 1988 and the Australian Privacy Principles.</p>
        <h2>Information we collect</h2>
        <p>When you use our website or contact us, we may collect your name, email address, phone number, company name, and details about your print management requirements. This information is collected when you submit a contact form, request a quote, or sign up for a free trial.</p>
        <h2>How we use your information</h2>
        <p>We use your information to respond to enquiries, provide quotes, arrange free trials, and send relevant product information. We do not sell or share your personal information with third parties except as necessary to provide the services you have requested.</p>
        <h2>Third-party services</h2>
        <p>We use ActiveCampaign (based in the United States) to manage contact form submissions and email communications. We use Google Analytics to understand how visitors use our website. We use Cloudflare for website hosting and security. Each of these services has its own privacy policy governing how they handle data.</p>
        <h2>Printix service</h2>
        <p>When you use the Printix cloud print management service, your print management data is handled by Tungsten Automation (the developer of Printix) under their own privacy policy and terms of service. We recommend reviewing the Printix privacy policy before starting a trial or subscription.</p>
        <h2>Cookies</h2>
        <p>Our website uses cookies for analytics purposes (Google Analytics). You can control cookie settings through your browser preferences.</p>
        <h2>Data security</h2>
        <p>We take reasonable steps to protect personal information from misuse, interference, and loss, and from unauthorised access, modification, or disclosure.</p>
        <h2>Your rights</h2>
        <p>You have the right to access, correct, or request deletion of your personal information. To make a request, contact us at the details below.</p>
        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p>If you have questions about this privacy policy or how we handle your personal information, please <a href="/contact">contact us</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <style is:inline>
    .prose h2{font-size:20px;font-weight:700;margin-top:32px;margin-bottom:12px}
    .prose p{font-size:15px;line-height:1.8;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:16px}
    .prose a{color:var(--brand);font-weight:600}
  </style>
</BaseLayout>
